<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>{% if title %}{{ title }} · {% endif %}Financial Hot Issues Daily</title>
  <meta name="description" content="마틴을 위한 글로벌 금융·재테크 핫이슈 분석 블로그" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; background-color: #060b1a; color:#f6f6f6; }
    body { margin:0; min-height:100vh; background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(141, 99, 255,0.25), transparent 55%), #030513; color:#e8ebf3; }
    main { padding: 32px clamp(16px, 3vw, 64px); max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }
    a { color:#9ddfff; text-decoration:none; }
    header { border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); margin-bottom:32px; }
    footer { margin-top:64px; font-size:0.85rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
    .issue-card { border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding:24px; border-radius: 18px; margin-bottom: 24px; background: rgba(8,11,26,0.8); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.35); }
    .issue-card h3 { margin-top:0; font-size:1.35rem; }
    .tags { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; margin-top:8px; }
    .tag { font-size:0.8rem; padding:4px 10px; border-radius:999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
    .issue-meta { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:0.85rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin-bottom:12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main>
    {{ content | safe }}
    <footer>
      <p>Cloudflare Pages + Eleventy · 매일 글로벌 금융 핫이슈 5개 요약</p>
      <p>마틴을 위한 자동화된 리서치/작성 워크플로</p>
    </footer>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
